.jpg","stars_count":5,"text":"<p>I was unsure at first, but I’m so glad I ordered. Beautiful quality, lovely packaging, and both pieces fit perfectly. I’ve already ordered again.<\/p>","author":"Siobhán K.","author_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/510155f0668b5ed0f414101a367f504c.jpg","hide_author_image":true,"verify":"5 days ago"}},"testimonial_NfKrKr":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Create_an_ultra-realistic_candid_customer_202605162051_45610788-13e6-4ce7-993f-19bbb5cfef1d.jpg","stars_count":5,"text":"<p>I contacted customer support about sizing before ordering and they were incredibly helpful. The cardigan fits perfectly and feels wonderfully comfortable.<\/p>","author":"Gráinne W.","author_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/90d7ebc69d293d9ee466403290c39e66.jpg","hide_author_image":true,"verify":"1 week ago"}},"testimonial_Vf8Fmm":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Create_an_ultra-realistic_casual_mirror_202605162101_1.jpg","stars_count":5,"text":"<p>After wearing the sweater regularly for months, it has held up beautifully. The fabric keeps its shape, the stitching still looks perfect, and it remains just as comfortable as when it arrived.<\/p>","author":"Aoife T.","author_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/597acd5125a7861edbe403560b767d66.jpg","hide_author_image":true,"verify":"6 days ago"}},"testimonial_hpHKet":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/also_make_sure_the_packiging_202605162051.jpg","stars_count":5,"text":"<p>My package arrived quickly and looked beautifully presented. I’m very happy with the dress and the overall quality.<\/p>","author":"Mary O.","author_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/ddb2da4fa5af983cdd8d6b28d34b75fe.jpg","hide_author_image":true,"verify":"3 days ago"}},"testimonial_cpTEk6":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/remove_the_neckless_from_this_202605171623.jpg","stars_count":5,"text":"<p>The dress looks beautiful on and feels very flattering. I’ve washed it a few times now and it still looks just as lovely as when it arrived.<\/p>","author":"Eileen D.","author_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/b87385ce4f05ea32e9146cfb97ca54c2.jpg","hide_author_image":true,"verify":"4 days ago"}},"testimonial_VTKTwW":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/make_it_look_like_the_202605162108.jpg","stars_count":5,"text":"<p>Beautiful quality and so comfortable. I wore it for lunch with my daughter and felt lovely in it all day.<\/p>","author":"Bríd C.","author_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/e427d13318ea117e896cfe8e48ef7bfc.jpg","hide_author_image":true,"verify":"2 hours ago"}}},"block_order":["heading_zQzBpk","sub_heading_8Tg8dc","sub_heading_Vhrdkf","heading_QDJ6tF","testimonial_PhiNje","testimonial_EkMKfy","testimonial_YBKrzt","testimonial_NfKrKr","testimonial_Vf8Fmm","testimonial_hpHKet","testimonial_cpTEk6","testimonial_VTKTwW"],"custom_css":[],"name":"SS - Testimonials #42","settings":{"content_align":"center","content_align_mobile":"center","slider_view":3.5,"slider_view_mobile":1.2,"slider_gap":30,"slider_gap_mobile":24,"slider_mt":52,"slider_mt_mobile":32,"slide_padding_advanced":false,"slide_padding_horizontal":20,"slide_padding_horizontal_mobile":20,"slide_padding_vertical":20,"slide_padding_vertical_mobile":20,"slide_radius":30,"slide_border_thickness":0,"slide_shadow":false,"slide_shadow_color":"#959da5","slide_content_align":"left","slide_content_align_mobile":"left","image_radius":30,"image_border_thickness":0,"image_ratio":"square","image_ratio_mobile":"square","verify_icon":false,"verify_icon_size":18,"verify_icon_size_mobile":18,"verify_bg":false,"verify_radius":100,"verify_border_thickness":0,"verify_mt":16,"verify_mt_mobile":16,"verify":"","verify_custom":false,"verify_font":"josefin_sans_n4","verify_size":12,"verify_size_mobile":12,"verify_height":130,"text_custom":false,"text_font":"josefin_sans_n4","text_size":16,"text_size_mobile":14,"text_height":150,"text_mt":16,"text_mt_mobile":16,"author_custom":false,"author_font":"josefin_sans_n4","author_size":18,"author_size_mobile":16,"author_height":130,"slide_stars_icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/moira-eileen-green-star-icon.png","slide_stars_size":20,"slide_stars_size_mobile":18,"slide_stars_mt":12,"slide_stars_mt_mobile":12,"author_image_size":60,"author_image_size_mobile":56,"author_image_radius":100,"author_image_border_thickness":0,"arrow_show_desktop":true,"arrow_show_mobile":false,"arrow_size":48,"arrow_size_mobile":38,"arrow_icon_size":10,"arrow_icon_size_mobile":8,"arrow_radius":100,"arrow_border_thickness":0,"arrow_hover_effect":"color","arrow_mt":40,"arrow_mt_mobile":32,"image_border_color":"#121212","text_color":"#121212","author_color":"#121212","slide_stars_color":"#121212","slide_bg_color":"#f3f3f3","slide_border_color":"#121212","verify_color":"#121212","verify_icon_checkmark_color":"#ffffff","verify_icon_color":"#2f80ed","verify_bg_color":"#eef6ff","verify_border_color":"#121212","author_image_color":"#ffffff","author_image_bg_color":"#121212","author_image_border_color":"#121212","arrow_color":"#7b7b7b","arrow_hover_color":"#7b7b7b","arrow_bg_color":"#f3f3f3","arrow_bg_hover_color":"#f7f7f7","arrow_border_color":"#c7c7c7","arrow_border_hover_color":"#c7c7c7","background_style":"solid","background_color":"#ffffff","background_gradient":"linear-gradient(180deg, #FFFFFF 0%, #F2F2F2 100%)","border_color":"#121212","margin_top":0,"margin_bottom":0,"margin_horizontal":0,"margin_horizontal_mobile":0,"padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36,"padding_horizontal":5,"padding_horizontal_mobile":1.5,"full_width":true,"content_width":1200,"border_thickness":0,"section_radius":0,"lazy":true}},"testimonials_TkkKtN":{"type":"testimonials","blocks":{"testimonial_Ugyn6d":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"icon":"5-stars","testimonial":"<p>I was unsure about spending nearly €120 on a pair of sandals and a summer dress from a brand I hadn’t ordered from before, but I’m genuinely delighted I gave it a chance. The quality was far better than I expected and everything arrived beautifully wrapped as well. The sandals are wonderfully comfortable and the dress fits perfectly for the warmer weather. I’ve since placed another order and I’m just as pleased.<\/p>","author":"Bríd C.","author_info":"Clonakilty, Cork"}},"testimonial_DBNeiE":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"icon":"5-stars","testimonial":"<p>The parcel arrived much quicker than I expected, only a few days to Waterford, and everything was packed with great care. The cardigan feels wonderfully made and like it will last for years.<\/p>","author":"Siobhán K.","author_info":"Waterford City, Waterford"}},"testimonial_PiqxzW":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"icon":"5-stars","testimonial":"<p>I had to contact customer support regarding sizing before ordering and they were incredibly helpful and patient. The blouse fits beautifully and is very comfortable to wear.<\/p>","author":"Deirdre P.","author_info":"Ballsbridge, Dublin"}},"testimonial_CeFFWn":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"icon":"5-stars","testimonial":"<p>After wearing the trousers regularly for several months now, I can honestly say they’ve held up beautifully. The stitching is still perfect, the fabric hasn’t lost its shape at all, and they remain as comfortable as the day they arrived. Proper long-lasting clothing is difficult to come by nowadays.<\/p>","author":"Gráinne W.","author_info":"Kilkenny City, Kilkenny"}},"testimonial_qzrz69":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"icon":"5-stars","testimonial":"<p>What struck me first was how lovely the presentation was when the package arrived. Everything was folded neatly and the material felt substantial straight away. The dress itself is elegant without being fussy and you can tell real care has gone into making it. I’ve already had compliments the few times I’ve worn it.<\/p>","author":"Aoife T.","author_info":"Ennis, Clare"}}},"block_order":["testimonial_Ugyn6d","testimonial_DBNeiE","testimonial_PiqxzW","testimonial_CeFFWn","testimonial_qzrz69"],"disabled":true,"custom_css":["\/* Review tekst aanpassen *\/.testimonials-slider__text .rte-setting p {font-size: 15px; \/* pas aan indien je het kleiner\/groter wilt *\/ line-height: 1.6;}"," \/* Optioneel: iets elegantere uitstraling *\/.testimonials-slider__text {font-weight: 400;}"," \/* Testimonials sterren groen maken *\/span.testimonial-stars {color: #00b67b !important;}"],"name":"t:sections.testimonials.presets.testimonials.name","settings":{"title":"Loved by Our Customers","align_text":"center","round_images":true,"color_background":"#f9f9f9","color_text":"#1c1d1d"}},"product-recommendations":{"type":"product-recommendations","custom_css":[".grid-product__price .grid-product__price--original {color: #7d7d7d !important;}",".grid-product__price {color: #1fb56c !important;}"],"settings":{"product_recommendations_heading":"Add More Favourites and Save 10% Today","related_count":6,"products_per_row":3}},"advanced_content_FykA6w":{"type":"advanced-content","blocks":{"image_fXMdzg":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/479bbf9e-5d1e-42b7-a3c0-fd6f814e4b4d.png","link":"","width":"50%","alignment":"center"}},"liquid_gnCdqT":{"type":"liquid","settings":{"code":"<h2>TIMELESS STYLE, CHOSEN WITH CARE<\/h2>\n<p>At Moira & Eileen Boutique, we choose soft, flattering pieces for real women and real life. Styles that feel comfortable, feminine, and beautifully timeless.<\/p>\n<p>Inspired by Moira and her granddaughter Eileen, our boutique is built around care, confidence, and everyday elegance.<\/p>\n<p>To speed up our sale, we are offering discounts of up to 70%!<\/p>","width":"50%","alignment":"center"}}},"block_order":["image_fXMdzg","liquid_gnCdqT"],"name":"t:sections.advanced-content.presets.custom_content.name","settings":{"full_width":false,"space_around":true,"lazyload_images":true}},"advanced_content_pRinRT":{"type":"advanced-content","blocks":{"liquid_Vw9kHA":{"type":"liquid","disabled":true,"settings":{"code":"<style>\n\n\/* SECTION *\/\n.custom-usp-section {\n  background: #ffffff;\n  padding: 55px 20px;\n}\n\n\/* GRID *\/\n.custom-usp-grid {\n  max-width: 1200px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);\n\n  gap: 40px;\n\n  text-align: center;\n}\n\n\/* ITEM *\/\n.custom-usp-item {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n}\n\n\/* FILLED CIRCLE *\/\n.custom-usp-icon {\n  width: 82px;\n  height: 82px;\n\n  border-radius: 999px;\n\n  background: #9C8B7A;\n\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n\n  margin-bottom: 18px;\n\n  transition: all 0.25s ease;\n}\n\n\/* HOVER *\/\n.custom-usp-item:hover .custom-usp-icon {\n  transform: translateY(-3px);\n}\n\n\/* ICONS *\/\n.custom-usp-icon img {\n  width: 36px;\n  height: 36px;\n\n  object-fit: contain;\n\n  filter: brightness(0) invert(1);\n  opacity: 0.95;\n}\n\n\/* TEXT *\/\n.custom-usp-title {\n  color: #9C8B7A;\n\n  font-size: 22px;\n  line-height: 1.25;\n\n  letter-spacing: 1.5px;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n\n  font-weight: 400;\n\n  font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;\n}\n\n\/* MOBILE *\/\n@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {\n\n  .custom-usp-section {\n    padding: 45px 20px;\n  }\n\n  .custom-usp-grid {\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n\n    gap: 50px 25px;\n  }\n\n  .custom-usp-icon {\n    width: 80px;\n    height: 80px;\n  }\n\n  .custom-usp-icon img {\n    width: 34px;\n    height: 34px;\n  }\n\n  .custom-usp-title {\n    font-size: 18px;\n    letter-spacing: 1.4px;\n  }\n}\n\n<\/style>\n\n<div class=\"custom-usp-section\">\n\n  <div class=\"custom-usp-grid\">\n\n    <!-- ECO -->\n    <div class=\"custom-usp-item\">\n\n      <div class=\"custom-usp-icon\">\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0662\/8488\/0137\/files\/eco-friendly-svgrepo-com.svg?v=1778707287\" alt=\"Eco Friendly\">\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"custom-usp-title\">\n        Eco-Friendly\n      <\/div>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n    <!-- FREE SHIPPING -->\n    <div class=\"custom-usp-item\">\n\n      <div class=\"custom-usp-icon\">\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0662\/8488\/0137\/files\/truck-svgrepo-com.svg?v=1778707287\" alt=\"Free Shipping\">\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"custom-usp-title\">\n        Free Shipping\n      <\/div>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n    <!-- EASY RETURNS -->\n    <div class=\"custom-usp-item\">\n\n      <div class=\"custom-usp-icon\">\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0662\/8488\/0137\/files\/30-days.png?v=1778707287\" alt=\"Easy Returns\">\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"custom-usp-title\">\n        Easy Returns\n      <\/div>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n    <!-- SECURE PAYMENT -->\n    <div class=\"custom-usp-item\">\n\n      <div class=\"custom-usp-icon\">\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0662\/8488\/0137\/files\/secure-payment-svgrepo-com.svg?v=1778707287\" alt=\"Secure Payment\">\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"custom-usp-title\">\n        Secure Payment\n      <\/div>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n  <\/div>\n\n<\/div>","width":"100%","alignment":"center"}}},"block_order":["liquid_Vw9kHA"],"disabled":true,"name":"t:sections.advanced-content.presets.custom_content.name","settings":{"full_width":true,"space_around":false,"lazyload_images":false}},"sub":{"type":"product-full-width","disabled":true,"settings":{"max_width":true}},"text_columns_zrQrWM":{"type":"text-columns","blocks":{"text_block_JYJbmm":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_image":true,"image_mask":"none","image_width":70,"title":"Expresslevering wereldwijd","text":"<p>We leveren wereldwijd met een veilige, getraceerde verzendmethode, voor de snelste en meest betrouwbare service. Gratis verzending voor bestellingen van meer dan €100 in Nederland, België en Duitsland | €150 voor de rest van de wereld.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}},"text_block_ViKUfr":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_image":true,"image_mask":"none","image_width":70,"title":"Koop nu, betaal later","text":"<p>Klarna Pay Later geeft je extra flexibiliteit bij het betalen van je bestelling omdat je binnen 30 dagen kunt betalen. Probeer je broek eerst uit en beslis dan of je hem wilt houden. <\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}},"text_block_hpc7VW":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_image":true,"image_mask":"none","image_width":70,"title":"14 dagen retour","text":"<p>Past niet? - Geen probleem! Je kunt altijd retourneren of ruilen. We bieden een retour- of omruilbeleid van 14 dagen als je om wat voor reden dan ook niet tevreden bent met je bestelling.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["text_block_JYJbmm","text_block_ViKUfr","text_block_hpc7VW"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"","align_text":"center","divider":false}},"faq_adDLaN":{"type":"faq","blocks":{"question_AEJMtz":{"type":"question","disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"Do you offer free shipping?","text":"<p>Yes, we are pleased to offer complimentary shipping on all orders. Every parcel is sent with <strong>An Post<\/strong> and includes tracking, so your order arrives safely and without any additional cost.<\/p>"}},"question_7H9VxL":{"type":"question","disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"Can I return an item if it does not fit or if I am not satisfied?","text":"<p>Of course. You may return your order within 30 days of receiving it. Items must be unworn, undamaged, and in their original condition.<\/p><p>Simply contact us via our Contact Page or email us directly at <a><strong>info@moiraeileenboutique.com<\/strong><\/a>, and we will gladly guide you through the return process.<\/p>"}},"question_hXnGAn":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"How can I track my order?","text":"<p>Once your order has been processed, you will receive a confirmation email containing your personal tracking number.<br\/><br\/>You can track your parcel at any time by visiting our <br\/><a href=\"https:\/\/vpg2hs-p2.myshopify.com\/apps\/parcelpanel\/\" target=\"_blank\">Order Tracking Page<\/a>.<br\/><br\/>Simply enter your tracking details to see the latest delivery updates.<\/p>"}},"question_P6gMr4":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"How do I choose the right size?","text":"<p>Each product includes a detailed size guide to help you find the best fit. If you are between sizes, we recommend choosing the larger size for added comfort.<\/p><p>If you are unsure, our customer care team is always happy to assist.<\/p>"}},"question_7fzArK":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"What payment methods do you accept?","text":"<p>You can complete your purchase securely using the following payment methods:<\/p><p>• Visa<br\/>• Mastercard<br\/>• American Express<br\/>• Apple Pay<br\/>• Google Pay<br\/>• Shop Pay<\/p><p>All payments are processed through secure and trusted payment providers.<\/p>"}},"question_73x3Pf":{"type":"question","disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"Is my payment secure?","text":"<p>Yes, your payment details are fully protected. We use industry standard SSL encryption to ensure your information remains safe and secure throughout the checkout process.<\/p>"}},"question_xyhRfD":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"How long does shipping take?","text":"<p>Orders are processed and dispatched within 24 hours on business days.<\/p><p>Delivery times may vary depending on your location, but we always strive to get your order to you as quickly as possible.<\/p><p>Once your order is on its way, you will receive a confirmation email with tracking details so you can follow your parcel at any time.<\/p>"}},"question_fWQXQc":{"type":"question","disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"How can I contact you if I have questions?","text":"<p>Our customer care team is always happy to assist you. You can contact us via our Contact Page or email us directly at <a><strong>info@moiraeileenboutique.com<\/strong><\/a>.<\/p><p>We aim to respond to all enquiries within 24 hours.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["question_AEJMtz","question_7H9VxL","question_hXnGAn","question_P6gMr4","question_7fzArK","question_73x3Pf","question_xyhRfD","question_fWQXQc"],"name":"t:sections.faq.presets.faq.name","settings":{"title":"FAQs"}},"advanced_content_aYHaYi":{"type":"advanced-content","blocks":{"liquid_e6ckgL":{"type":"liquid","settings":{"code":"<div class=\"moira-trust-section\">\n  <div class=\"moira-trust-grid\">\n\n    <div class=\"moira-trust-item\">\n      <div class=\"moira-trust-icon\">\n        <img \n          src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0662\/8488\/0137\/files\/Flag-map_of_Ireland_svg.png?v=1778712672\" \n          alt=\"Based in Ireland\"\n        >\n      <\/div>\n      <h3>BASED IN IRELAND<\/h3>\n      <p>\n        Proudly created for women across Ireland, with thoughtful styles and a boutique feel close to home.\n      <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"moira-trust-item\">\n      <div class=\"moira-trust-icon moira-css-icon\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n          <path d=\"M14 22h26v22H14z\"><\/path>\n          <path d=\"M40 30h8l6 7v7H40z\"><\/path>\n          <circle cx=\"23\" cy=\"47\" r=\"4\"><\/circle>\n          <circle cx=\"48\" cy=\"47\" r=\"4\"><\/circle>\n          <path d=\"M18 17h18\"><\/path>\n          <path d=\"M10 28h10\"><\/path>\n          <path d=\"M8 34h12\"><\/path>\n        <\/svg>\n      <\/div>\n      <h3>FREE SHIPPING<\/h3>\n      <p>\n        Enjoy complimentary tracked delivery throughout Ireland with An Post and clear order updates.\n      <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"moira-trust-item\">\n      <div class=\"moira-trust-icon moira-css-icon\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n          <path d=\"M18 18h28v34H18z\"><\/path>\n          <path d=\"M24 14v8\"><\/path>\n          <path d=\"M40 14v8\"><\/path>\n          <path d=\"M18 26h28\"><\/path>\n          <path d=\"M25 37h14\"><\/path>\n          <path d=\"M25 44h10\"><\/path>\n        <\/svg>\n      <\/div>\n      <h3>30-DAY RETURNS<\/h3>\n      <p>\n        Not quite the right fit? You can return your order within 30 days for peace of mind.\n      <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"moira-trust-item\">\n      <div class=\"moira-trust-icon moira-css-icon\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n          <path d=\"M14 18h36v24H26l-10 8v-8h-2z\"><\/path>\n          <path d=\"M23 27h18\"><\/path>\n          <path d=\"M23 34h13\"><\/path>\n        <\/svg>\n      <\/div>\n      <h3>PERSONAL CARE<\/h3>\n      <p>\n        Our team is here to help with sizing, orders, and questions whenever you need us.\n      <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<style>\n  .moira-trust-section {\n    width: 100%;\n    padding: 34px 18px 38px;\n    background: #ffffff;\n  }\n\n  .moira-trust-grid {\n    max-width: 1040px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);\n    gap: 24px;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  .moira-trust-item {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    align-items: center;\n    padding: 8px 10px;\n    transition: transform 0.28s ease, opacity 0.28s ease;\n  }\n\n  .moira-trust-item:hover {\n    transform: translateY(-6px);\n  }\n\n  .moira-trust-icon {\n    width: 78px;\n    height: 78px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background-color: #A49483;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    margin: 0 auto 16px;\n    transition: transform 0.28s ease, box-shadow 0.28s ease, background-color 0.28s ease;\n  }\n\n  .moira-trust-item:hover .moira-trust-icon {\n    transform: scale(1.05);\n    box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(164, 148, 131, 0.24);\n    background-color: #9C8B7B;\n  }\n\n  .moira-trust-icon img {\n    width: 45px;\n    height: 45px;\n    object-fit: contain;\n    display: block;\n    filter: grayscale(100%) brightness(0) invert(1);\n    opacity: 0.96;\n  }\n\n  .moira-css-icon svg {\n    width: 40px;\n    height: 40px;\n    fill: none;\n    stroke: #ffffff;\n    stroke-width: 2.4;\n    stroke-linecap: round;\n    stroke-linejoin: round;\n  }\n\n  .moira-trust-item h3 {\n    margin: 0 0 10px;\n    font-size: 20px;\n    letter-spacing: 2.1px;\n    line-height: 1.25;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    color: #A49483;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n  }\n\n  .moira-trust-item p {\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    line-height: 1.55;\n    color: #222222;\n    max-width: 230px;\n  }\n\n  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {\n    .moira-trust-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n      gap: 28px 20px;\n      max-width: 640px;\n    }\n  }\n\n  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {\n    .moira-trust-section {\n      padding: 26px 14px 30px;\n    }\n\n    .moira-trust-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n      gap: 26px 14px;\n    }\n\n    .moira-trust-item {\n      padding: 0 4px;\n    }\n\n    .moira-trust-item:hover {\n      transform: none;\n    }\n\n    .moira-trust-icon {\n      width: 64px;\n      height: 64px;\n      margin-bottom: 12px;\n    }\n\n    .moira-trust-item:hover .moira-trust-icon {\n      transform: none;\n      box-shadow: none;\n      background-color: #A49483;\n    }\n\n    .moira-trust-icon img {\n      width: 37px;\n      height: 37px;\n    }\n\n    .moira-css-icon svg {\n      width: 34px;\n      height: 34px;\n      stroke-width: 2.3;\n    }\n\n    .moira-trust-item h3 {\n      font-size: 15.5px;\n      letter-spacing: 1.7px;\n      line-height: 1.25;\n      margin-bottom: 7px;\n    }\n\n    .moira-trust-item p {\n      font-size: 13.2px;\n      line-height: 1.45;\n      max-width: 150px;\n    }\n  }\n\n  @media screen and (max-width: 390px) {\n    .moira-trust-section {\n      padding: 24px 10px 28px;\n    }\n\n    .moira-trust-grid {\n      gap: 24px 10px;\n    }\n\n    .moira-trust-icon {\n      width: 60px;\n      height: 60px;\n    }\n\n    .moira-trust-icon img {\n      width: 34px;\n      height: 34px;\n    }\n\n    .moira-css-icon svg {\n      width: 31px;\n      height: 31px;\n    }\n\n    .moira-trust-item h3 {\n      font-size: 14px;\n      letter-spacing: 1.5px;\n    }\n\n    .moira-trust-item p {\n      font-size: 12.7px;\n      max-width: 135px;\n    }\n  }\n<\/style>","width":"100%","alignment":"center"}}},"block_order":["liquid_e6ckgL"],"name":"t:sections.advanced-content.presets.custom_content.name","settings":{"full_width":false,"space_around":true,"lazyload_images":true}},"text_with_icons_PQ998N":{"type":"text-with-icons","blocks":{"text_block_faGPgH":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"icon":"truck","title":"FREE SHIPPING","text":"<p>Enjoy complimentary premium shipping on every order with An Post. Tracking is included, with fast and reliable delivery and no hidden costs.<\/p>"}},"text_block_qMR7pm":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"icon":"package","title":"30 DAYS RETURN","text":"<p>Not quite the right fit? You can return or exchange your item within 30 days if it is not exactly what you expected.<\/p>"}},"text_block_NiDfRL":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"icon":"chat","title":"CUSTOMER SERVICE","text":"<p>Our team is always here to help. Feel free to contact us anytime at <a><strong>info@moiraeileenboutique<\/strong><\/a> and we will be happy to assist you.<br\/><br\/><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_block_faGPgH","text_block_qMR7pm","text_block_NiDfRL"],"disabled":true,"name":"t:common.text_with_icons.presets.text_with_icons.name","settings":{"title":"","align_text":"center","desktop_columns_per_row":3,"icon_color":"#000000","button_label":"","button_link":"","divider":false}},"recently-viewed":{"type":"recently-viewed","disabled":true,"settings":{"recent_count":5}},"collection-return":{"type":"collection-return","disabled":true,"settings":{}}},"order":["main","ss_testimonials_42_AhNMbz","testimonials_TkkKtN","product-recommendations","advanced_content_FykA6w","advanced_content_pRinRT"